data.description: SOLD AS-IS. Welcome Home! 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 2 car garage single story POOL home on a ONE AND HALF ACRE CORNER LOT located in sought-after Bear Track Ranch community in Ocala where you are just minutes from shopping, restaurants, schools, and a short drive to Ocala International Airport! This home has wonderful curb appeal situation on an oversized one and half acre corner lot lined with beautifully manicured live oaks and a long driveway welcoming you home. When you walk in you will be welcomed by bright natural light, high ceilings, and beautiful tile flooring in your formal family room overlooking the stunning view of the enclosed patio/pool area perfect for any family. This home offers many great features including an open split bedroom floor plan, open kitchen overlooking the living room, a formal family room, a formal dining room, a private master bedroom wing, guest bedroom wings, an indoor utility room, screened in patio/pool area, 2 car garage, and a HUGE BACKYARD. The master bedroom offers wood flooring, tray ceilings, plenty of space, a walk-in closet and easy access to the pool with sliding glass doors leading out to enclosed patio/pool deck. In the kitchen you will find granite countertops with bar top seating, stainless steel appliances, vaulted ceilings, a breakfast nook, and plenty of space for hosting overlooking the living room! This home is perfect for any family given how much space it has to offer! Speaking of perfect, wait till you walk out back to your HUGE POOL BACKYARD! Features include a screened in enclosed pool with plenty of deck space for family gatherings, cookouts, and yard space for your pets! This home offers many beautiful features including: Roof (2010), Trane AC System (2020), Water Heater (2019). The home is on Well and Septic. Bear Track Ranch is a well maintained NO HOA community. Located close to shopping, restaurants, schools and an easy commute to the Ocala International Airport. You won't want to miss this home as it will go quick! Schedule your showing today for this beautiful home! Seller is offering the Buyer a 1 year Home Warranty. SOLD AS-IS.
